target: You're welcome. Have a great day!
context: <user> Hello, I need a train to Peterborough from Cambridge please <system> Which day would you like to travel? <user> I would like to travel on friday, and arrive by 14:45 <system> TR9859 would fit your needs shall i book it ? <user> Actually, no need to book. But, can I get the travel time and the price of the ticket please? <system> Of course. The travel time is 50 minutes. The price is 16.50 pounds. Would you like any other information? <user> Yes, I'm also looking for places to go in town. <system> Sure, I can help you with that. What kind of attraction were you looking for?<user> I would like to find a museum in the centre of town. <system> There are many. Would you like me to recommend one for you?<user> Yes, please. What is your favorite museum? I'd like their address and postcode. You're a lifesaver! <system> The Museum of Archaeology and Anthropology is excellent. They're at University of Cambridge, Downing Street in postcode cb23dz. Is there anything else I can help you with?<user> Um... no, I think I should be good with that. Thanks. <system>
